For an interesting twist...Finely dice three garlic cloves and saute in 1/4 cup of olive oil until goldenbrown. Discard the garlics and spread the garlic oil of the open sides of the bread before lightly baking. Then spread the artichoke mixture and proceed. Hey, add a can of drained anchovies for an additional kick. Wheeee.

