Wonderful, simple and fast. I used the canned artichoke bottoms instead of the artichoke hearts because I don't like the leaves. I finely chopped the whole can of the bottoms. I agree, the bread should be baked on both sides first, the put the mixture on the bread and I baked them instead of broiling for fear I would forget them in the broiler and ruin them. They were all gone in no time. Can't wait to make them again. They are perfect for a party because as they cool , they are still delicious.

